author: @ramulal6151
text: s = """w'o"w""" repr(s) # Output: '\'w\\\'o"w\'' str(s) # Output: 'w\'o"w' eval(str(s)) == s # Gives a SyntaxError eval(repr(s)) == s # Output: True
